title: German States United: Defense Against British Aggression - Napoleonic: Total War 3 Mod Gameplay
description:
British and Russian forces have united to wage war against the German States.  The Germans must stand together, or die divided.  This is a 3v3 in Napoleonic: Total War 3.  Enjoy the Battle :D

Napoleonic: Total War 3 is a Mod for Napoleon Total War.
Mod Link: http://www.moddb.com/mods/napoleonic-total-war-3
